      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, meticulously maintained to the highest possible standards since the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with absolutely no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. The body panels are perfectly aligned, reflecting a life spent in a climate-controlled garage. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and free of any creasing, while the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a full, documented service history from authorized specialists. It drives with the tightness and precision of a brand-new vehicle, with no rattles, leaks, or delayed shifts. Every electronic component, sensor, and luxury feature functions flawlessly. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to acquire an example that has been pampered as a collector's item rather than a daily driver. Includes all original manuals, two sets of keys, and a custom car cover.",
